Pre-Game Insights: Ireland's men's T20 International squads were announced, including Joshua Little as the 15th member for the T20 World Cup following his IPL stint.
The team aims to make an impact in the upcoming series against Pakistan, the Tri-Series, and the T20 World Cup.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match against Pakistan is part of a three-match series in Dublin starting on May 10, 2024.
